{
  "stem": "2723.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I didn't understand what was front or back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Bizarre underwear, bizarre outerwear, and these damned clogs that became the bane of my existence.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And finally, I think what looked like incredibly long spans of time, I stood in front of somebody who was tattooing my arm, and I became, then, a number, a cipher, which is still there.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I was never tempted to remove it because I think it served its purpose in my life.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It reminded me when I thought I was badly done by.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was very tall for my age.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I was powerfully built.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And indeed, miraculously, I was taken to a barrack, which apparently belonged to the kitchen staff.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "By that time, I was suddenly terribly, terribly alone and frightened.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I didn't know a soul around me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I know that my second shock came when I recognized the face as being the daughter of my grandmother's cook.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why did I recognize her?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She had hair.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She was one of the unfortunate girls who went there in '42, had lived through the awful apprenticeship and battled through, and was, in fact, in charge.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she was a capo, which was an office bearer.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was so happy to see that face.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I thought, oh, well, now everything will change.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "A, she will tell me, what is this?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Where am I?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "B, she might tell me something about my mother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I sent word to her through someone that I was in hole in the wall, second on the left, which was the hole in the wall that became mine, shared with four others.",
      "word_count": 33
    }
  ],
